                    src="https://draftsim.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Irascible-Wolverine_0130_EN.png" alt="" />
            </figure>
            \n\n\n\n<figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img decoding="async" width="733" height="1024"
                    data-id="184579"
                    src="https://draftsim.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Make-Your-Own-Luck-733x1024.png" alt=""
                    class="wp-image-184579"
                    srcset="https://draftsim.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Make-Your-Own-Luck-733x1024.png 733w, https://draftsim.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Make-Your-Own-Luck-215x300.png 215w, https://draftsim.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Make-Your-Own-Luck-390x545.png 390w, https://draftsim.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Make-Your-Own-Luck-300x419.png 300w, https://draftsim.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Make-Your-Own-Luck.png 744w"
                    sizes="(max-width: 733px) 100vw, 733px" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure
                class="wp-block-image size-large">
                <img decoding="async" width="733" height="1024" data-id="184580"
                    src="https://draftsim.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Plan-the-Heist-733x1024.png" alt=""
                    class="wp-image-184580"
                    srcset="https://draftsim.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Plan-the-Heist-733x1024.png 733w, https://draftsim.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Plan-the-Heist-215x300.png 215w, https://draftsim.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Plan-the-Heist-390x545.png 390w, https://draftsim.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Plan-the-Heist-300x419.png 300w, https://draftsim.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Plan-the-Heist.png 744w"
                    sizes="(max-width: 733px) 100vw, 733px" />
            </figure>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Almost like <a href="https://draftsim.com/suspend-mtg/">suspending</a> a card
            without time counters. Plot allows you to
            shift the turn in which you pay for a card. This makes for big swings and easier double-spell turns.</p>
        \n\n\n\n
        <p>Here's an example: &#8220;You may pay <i class="mana-2"></i><i class="mana-r"></i> and exile this card from
            your
            hand. Cast it as a sorcery on a later turn without paying its mana cost. Plot only as a sorcery.&#8221;</p>
